snippet.title: SSCC Electric Vehicle Charging Infrastructure Webinar
snippet.description:
Join South Shore Clean Cities for the Electric Vehicle Charging Infrastructure Webinar. Learn from industry experts regarding charging options available, infrastructure requirements and benefits of investing charging stations at your house and workplace. Hear from South Shore Clean Cities how the Green Fleet Program could help assist with making the right choices to fit your fleet’s needs.

Speakers for the Webinar include:
   - Ryan Lisek, Project Manager, South Shore Clean Cities 
   - Brian Levin, Regional Director - Midwest, ChargePoint 
   - Josh Cohen, Director of Public Policy, Greenlots
   - John Truckenbrod, Founder & CEO, EV Energy Group
